{"id":478967,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":10,"day":11}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"155","ytitle":"","mtitle":"毛主席语录","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"三大纪律如下:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)一切行动听指挥；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)不拿群众一针一线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)一切缴获要归公。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八项注意如下:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)说话和气；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)买卖公平；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)借东西要还；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(四)损坏东西要赔；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(五)不打人骂人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(六)不损坏庄稼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(七)不调戏妇女；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(八)不虐待俘虏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《中国人民解放军总部关于重行颁布三大纪律八项注意的训令》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1966\\10\\66ab020101.JPG\">"}]}